### Update App Router Runtime Config from experimental-edge to edge

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/upgrading/codemods.mdx

This App Router specific codemod updates the `runtime` value in Route Segment Configs from the deprecated `experimental-edge` to the standardized `edge`. It helps maintain compatibility with the latest Next.js runtime environments.

```bash
npx @next/codemod@latest app-dir-runtime-config-experimental-edge .
```

```typescript
// Before transformation:
export const runtime = 'experimental-edge'
```

```typescript
// After transformation:
export const runtime = 'edge'
```

